HEADWORD: Altruistic
<hw>Al`tru*is"tic</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>altruiste</ets>, a. See <er>Altruism</er>..]</ety> <def>Regardful
of others; beneficent; unselfish; -- opposed to <ant>egoistic</ant> or
<ant>selfish</ant>.</def> <au>Bain.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Al`tru*is"tic*al*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

